data.description: Quaint cabin tucked in Sundance on 2.5 wooded acres near Broadway. This affordable 2 BD, 1 BA home would make a great full time residence, vacation home, or investment. Nice open living area with fireplace, eat-in kitchen, and large sliding door to the oversized deck.
